metadata.name: What a Life...
metadata.description:
The holy land gave off a sweet blue. Docile and fresh as a daisy. This blue is your life. You are a part of this blue with your character, view of life and emotions. You should create your own adventure with these values. Rustic evenings can leave you alone. Continue your own way. Whatever color your word is, don't be afraid to add them to your life.
Always keep you alive. Don't kill off your muse. Let life flow..
